				<h1 class="entry-title">Monsanto Cartoons Add Much Needed Humor to Some Not So Funny Issues</h1>
		
				<div class="entry-content">
			<div class="addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style " addthis:url='http://green.thefuntimesguide.com/2010/01/monsanto_scandal_cartoons.php' addthis:title='Monsanto Cartoons Add Much Needed Humor to Some Not So Funny Issues '><a class="addthis_button_facebook_like" fb:like:layout="button_count"></a><a class="addthis_button_tweet"></a><a class="addthis_button_google_plusone" g:plusone:size="medium"></a><a class="addthis_counter addthis_pill_style"></a></div><p>Monsanto, the multinational agricultural giant who sells 90% of the world&#8217;s genetically engineered seeds, <a target="_blank" href="http://www.triplepundit.com/2010/01/why-monsanto-might-be-worried/?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+TriplePundit+%28Triple+Pundit%29" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://www.triplepundit.com']);">has been in the news a lot this month</a>&#8230;and as usual, it&#8217;s not the kind of press they&#8217;d like to have.</p>
<p>We usually post a funny image, video, or story on <a href="http://green.thefuntimesguide.com/cgi-bin/mt4/mt-search.cgi?blog_id=25&amp;tag=funny&amp;limit=10" target="_blank">Fridays</a>. For that reason, we&#8217;re going to chuckle over some <a target="_blank" href="http://joemohrtoons.com/tag/monsanto/" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://joemohrtoons.com']);">incredible Monsanto illustrations</a> by the talented cartoonist, <a target="_blank" href="http://joemohrtoons.com/" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://joemohrtoons.com']);">Joe Mohr</a>.</p>
<p>&#8230;but we&#8217;re still going to file this one in the [not-so] funny Friday folder.</p>
<!-- Quick Adsense WordPress Plugin: http://techmilieu.com/quick-adsense -->
<div style="float:left;margin:0px 0px 0px 0;">
