</div>
</div>

<p>Read on below the cartoons to learn more about what they&#8217;re alluding to.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Monsanto-claus holds the world's seed supply hostage, via Joe Mohr" rel="lightbox[gallery14]" href="http://green.thefuntimesguide.com/images/blogs/monsanto-claus.jpg"><img width="485" height="311" align="" title="Monsanto-claus holds the world's seed supply hostage, via Joe Mohr" alt="monsanto-claus.jpg" src="http://green.thefuntimesguide.com/files/monsanto-claus-thumb-485x311-12370.jpg"/></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Monsanto would rather see Africans die than give them seeds, via Joe Mohr" rel="lightbox[gallery14]" href="http://green.thefuntimesguide.com/images/blogs/Monsanto-Africa-scandal.jpg"><img width="485" height="407" align="" title="Monsanto would rather see Africans die than give them seeds, via Joe Mohr" alt="Monsanto-Africa-scandal.jpg" src="http://green.thefuntimesguide.com/files/Monsanto-Africa-scandal-thumb-485x407-12372.jpg"/></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Monsanto GMO corn causes organ damage in mammals, via Joe Mohr" rel="lightbox[gallery14]" href="http://green.thefuntimesguide.com/images/blogs/Monsanto-Corn-Organ-Damage.jpg"><img width="485" height="567" align="" title="Monsanto GMO corn causes organ damage in mammals, via Joe Mohr" alt="Monsanto-Corn-Organ-Damage.jpg" src="http://green.thefuntimesguide.com/files/Monsanto-Corn-Organ-Damage-thumb-485x567-12374.jpg"/></a></p>
<p>
<!-- Quick Adsense WordPress Plugin: http://techmilieu.com/quick-adsense -->
<div style="float:none;margin:0px;">
<!-- LivingGreen_Middle_Content -->
<div class="ad-spacer"></div>                       
